  "content": {
    "prompt": "Using recursion, complete the power method so that it returns the value of a to the power of b.\nExamples:\n\n    power(3,4) => 81\n\n    power(2,8) => 256\n\n    power(1,1) => 1\n\n    power(9,0) => 1",
    "source_code": "public class JRecursionPower1{\n    static int power(int a, int b) {\n        if(b > 0){\n            return a * power(a, b-1);\n        }\n        return 1;\n    }\n    public static void main(String args[]){\n        JRecursionPower1 rp = new JRecursionPower1();\n        int a = 2, b=8;\n        System.out.println(\"The 8th power of 2 is: \" + rp.power(a,b));\n    }\n    \n}"
  },
